}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== *The FCC photos for this device appear to be the same as those for the :A90-9150V60-10 under ''[[NETGEAR]]'''s grantee code (FCC ID: PY312400224).
There are two ''[[Marvell]]'' 88E6065B-LAJ1 GbE Switch chips on the board in the FCC photos. :CPU: [[Lantiq]] TwinPass-E (PXB 4000 E) - GRX100 CPE Network Processor
The shell of the unit in the FCC photos shows the device branded :for [http://www.cincinnatibell.com/fioptics/ ''Cincinnati Bell'' Fioptics'] service.
The default IP for the device may be 192.168.1.1 or 192.168.200.1.
